EA servers are currently down, leaving FIFA 22 fans unable to play games online. The EA server status makes grim reading for fans, who have complained about not being able to connect to the servers. Independent website Down Detector has received thousands of reports that FIFA isn't working. The outage tracker monitors social mentions around certain topics to detect when services go down across the world. The Down Detector outage map shows that the FIFA and EA Sports issues are mainly affecting users in the UK and Europe. Other less popular EA games are also experiencing issues, such as Battlefield 2042 and Madden NFL. More to followâ€¦